<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Welcome to [Your Property Management System]!</title>
<style>
  /* Add your custom styles here */
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f7f7f7;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 20px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  h1 {
    color: #333;
  }

  p {
    color: #666;
  }

  .credentials {
    background-color: #f0f0f0;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .credentials p {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .signature {
    margin-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
    padding-top: 10px;
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to {{ sentenceCase(env('DEFAULT_BUSINESS_NAME')) }}!</h1>
    <p>Dear {{ recipientName }},</p>
    <p>Welcome to our platform! We're excited to have you on board as a tenant.</p>
    <p>You have been invited by your landlord, {{ landlordName }}, to join our property management system. Below are your login credentials:</p>
    <div class="credentials">
      <p><strong>Username:</strong> {{ tenantEmail }} </p>
      <p><strong>Password:</strong> {{ tenantPassword }}</p>
    </div>
    <p>Please use the provided credentials to log in to your account. We recommend changing your password after logging in for security purposes.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
    <p>Once again, welcome to {{ sentenceCase(env('DEFAULT_BUSINESS_NAME')) }}! We look forward to providing you with a seamless renting experience.</p>
    <div class="signature">
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>
        {{ sentenceCase(env('DEFAULT_EMAIL_NAME')) }}<br>
        {{ sentenceCase(env('DEFAULT_BUSINESS_NAME')) }} Team
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
